    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Ranged Tactics Toolbox pg. 26</em></p><p><strong>Aura</strong> faint evocation <strong>CL</strong> 8th</p><p><strong>Slot</strong> none; <strong>Price</strong> +2 bonus; <strong>Weight</strong> -</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><img src=\"modules/pf-content/assets/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" title=\"PFS Legal\" style=\"margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;\"><strong>Description</strong></h3>This special ability can be placed only on firearms or firearm ammunition. Whenever a <em>dazzling</em> weapon is fired, it emits an explosive flash that dazzles all foes adjacent to the bullet's path or within or adjacent to the cone of a scatter shot. This condition lasts a number of rounds equal to the weapon's enhancement bonus.</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><strong>Construction</strong></h3><strong>Requirements</strong> Craft Magic Arms and Armor, <em>flare burst</em><sup>APG</sup>; <strong>Price</strong> -</p>",
